title: Jyashin-chan Dropkick
description: Jyashin-chan Dropkick is a violent slapstick comedy about a delusional gothic lolita, Yurine, who summons a demon girl with the tail of a cobra, Jyashin-chan. They'll have to live together -- until Yurine finds a way to send Jyashin-chan back to hell, or until Jyashin-chan kills Yurine.
